			<div class="content" id="post-content-2692123">
									

<p>This might have come more from the heart than someone would expect. This is a story about how people change and their values change, and what's really important. GAW, to me, comes from a political place, and that's where I wanted to go to in this tale. I hope you like it.</p>
<p>And don't worry, I don't have any plans to write any more GAW anytime soon.</p>
<p>Edit: I also do not have any ideas for Mr. Bernie Sanders. Bluntfiend does, though.</p>

