<p>This was a lot, and I mean that in the best way. It did a lot to develop GAW and what they're about, differentiated them from AWCY? which is good, because I was worried about GAW becoming the lolrandom version of AWCY?, and those fears have been thoroughly dashed, with their similarities being nothing more than superficial as of this tale. Bones being Eli is just really cool to me, and it warmed this old homestuck's heart to see GAW's reaction to him.</p>
