				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1918720&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222987" alt="Scorpion451" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1918720)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpion451" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1918720); return false;" >Scorpion451</a></span> <span class="odate time_1479242267 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">15 Nov 2016 20:37</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2692201">
									

<p>Seconding much of this, but in a more enthusiastic fashion.</p>
<p>I'm loving GAW, and I think this piece in particular solidifies for me a big reason why: They're existentialists<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-926070-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-926070-1')">1</a></sup>. Nihilists stare into the abyss and see fear. Existentialists see a blank canvas.</p>
<p>The next step in their growth needs to be making them more than just a foil to AWCY, and this piece sets up an avenue for that growth rather nicely. While both in and out of universe their beginnings are a band of merry pranksters, their real potential lies in the same sort of nebulous, &quot;smiling punk&quot; zone as Anonymous- that odd place somewhere between a band of vigilantes with a vaguely noble cause and a bunch of cackling trolls looking for an excuse. There's a lot of depth to explore there, I think.</p>
<p>Side note: Eli and GAW are perfect together. Nice that it's found a place to belong. X3</p>
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="title">Footnotes</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-926070-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-926070-1')">1</a>. aka anti-nihilists</div>
</div>

