			<div class="content" id="post-content-2692545">
									

<p>I didn't walk into this realizing it was going to be GOW, but I enjoyed it thoroughly as the revelations came. 2721 was especially fun.</p>
<p>A hearty +1</p>
<p>I definitely see the issue with painting them a a reaction to AWCY?, even if that's the heart of this particular character's tale rather than that of the organization. I know they also enjoy taking the piss out of Wondertainment.</p>
<p>I think this is a good step towards characterizing them, especially including implications of what Bones is doing there in the first place. I also think the misters so far are good at conveying more character-driven stories than &quot;anti-GOI snark fest&quot; or even the &quot;Wondertainment-is-nuts&quot; story that drives his little misters, but that targeted-snark-pile is the pitfall to avoid.</p>

